  "Description": {
    "English": "A canister of the now-banned Vy'keen battle gas, traditionally inhaled on the eve of battle.<br><br>Purchase is <span class=\"name name-special\">illegal</span> at nearly all galactic trade terminals. Regular supply is only available within <span class=\"name name-fuel\">outlaw systems</span>.<br><br>Selling banned goods into commercially-regulated space may be <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">highly profitable</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一罐现今已被禁止的维吉恩战斗气体，传统上用于在战斗前吸入。<br><br>在几乎所有的星系贸易终端购买此产品都是<span class=\"name name-special\">非法的</span>。只有在<span class=\"name name-fuel\">亡命之徒恒星系</span>内才有正常供应。<br><br>将违禁品倒卖到受管制的宇宙空间可能会产生<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">高额利润</span>。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "一罐現已禁用的維金族戰鬥氣體，傳統上會在戰鬥前夕吸入。<br><br>在幾乎所有銀河交易終端站購買此物品，皆為<span class=\"name name-special\">違法</span>。僅可在<span class=\"name name-fuel\">亡命之徒星系</span>中取得穩定供貨。<br><br>將違禁物品販售到受商業管制的太空，有機會獲得<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">極高利潤</span>。"
  },
