  "PinObjectiveTip": {
    "English": "The sale of GrahGrah is highly regulated. Purchase is <span class=\"name name-special\">illegal</span> at most trade terminals.<br>Acquisition may be possible from <span class=\"name name-fuel\">Outlaw</span> systems.<br>Extreme caution must be used while transporting banned goods within regulated space.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "格拉格拉的销售处于严格的管控之下。在大部分终端中购买这种产品都是<span class=\"name name-special\">非法</span>的。<br>有一定可能可以从<span class=\"name name-fuel\">亡命之徒</span>的恒星系中获得。<br>在受管制的宇宙空间内运输违禁品时必须极其小心。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "嘎啦嘎啦的銷售受到高度管控。在大多數交易終端站購買此物品，皆為<span class=\"name name-special\">違法</span>。<br>可能在<span class=\"name name-fuel\">亡命之徒</span>星系獲得。<br>在受管制的太空內運輸違禁物品時，必須格外小心。"
